io.sarl.core

Event ParticipantJoined

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.sarl.lang.core.Event
      • io.sarl.core.ParticipantJoined
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public final class ParticipantJoined
extends Event
    Notifies other participants the member with agentID has effectively integrated the space. The event is fired within the default space of the context in which the agent entered a new space. The joining agent does not receive this event. The source of the event is the entering agent.
